{"type":"message","id":"d088ed3f","parentId":"7e5c91b9","timestamp":"2026-03-28T12:06:28.789Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_hv2Vm4G9hk1EkLfjjtucGkZO|fc_075abb85efaf918e0169c7c443a2f8819aad35f4452680fbef","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"usage: active_task_cli.py advance [-h] --path PATH [--status STATUS]\n                                  [--updated UPDATED] [--complete-current]\n                                  [--complete COMPLETE] [--current CURRENT]\n                                  [--promote-next] [--next NEXT]\n                                  [--append-completed APPEND_COMPLETED]\n                                  [--append-evidence APPEND_EVIDENCE]\n                                  [--set-blocker SET_BLOCKER]\n                                  [--clear-blockers]\n\noptions:\n  -h, --help            show this help message and exit\n  --path PATH           Path to ACTIVE_TASK.md\n  --status STATUS       New Status value\n  --updated UPDATED     Explicit Updated timestamp\n  --complete-current    Move existing Current item into Completed before other\n                        updates.\n  --complete COMPLETE   Compatibility alias: append the provided item to\n                        Completed.\n  --current CURRENT     Set the new Current item\n  --promote-next        Promote the first Next item into Current.\n  --next NEXT           Replace Next list; repeat for multiple items.\n  --append-completed APPEND_COMPLETED\n                        Append an item to Completed; repeat for multiple\n                        items.\n  --append-evidence APPEND_EVIDENCE\n                        Append an item to Evidence; repeat for multiple items.\n  --set-blocker SET_BLOCKER\n                        Replace Blockers with the provided item(s).\n  --clear-blockers      Clear Blockers.\n\n__OPENCLAW_ACTIVE_TASK_SHOW__\n{\n  \"path\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\",\n  \"status\": \"blocked\",\n  \"updated\": \"2026-03-28 20:00\",\n  \"current\": [\n    \"等待用户提供视频文件、飞书消息附件，或可访问的视频链接\"\n  ],\n  \"next\": [\n    \"收到视频后提取音轨并转写歌词\",\n    \"清洗歌词文本、按段落整理并生成文档\",\n    \"将文档发回当前飞书会话\"\n  ],\n  \"completed_count\": 1,\n  \"evidence_count\": 2,\n  \"blockers\": [\n    \"用户消息中未附带视频文件、附件 token 或可访问链接，暂时无法开始提取歌词\"\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":82,"aggregated":"usage: active_task_cli.py advance [-h] --path PATH [--status STATUS]\n                                  [--updated UPDATED] [--complete-current]\n                                  [--complete COMPLETE] [--current CURRENT]\n                                  [--promote-next] [--next NEXT]\n                                  [--append-completed APPEND_COMPLETED]\n                                  [--append-evidence APPEND_EVIDENCE]\n                                  [--set-blocker SET_BLOCKER]\n                                  [--clear-blockers]\n\noptions:\n  -h, --help            show this help message and exit\n  --path PATH           Path to ACTIVE_TASK.md\n  --status STATUS       New Status value\n  --updated UPDATED     Explicit Updated timestamp\n  --complete-current    Move existing Current item into Completed before other\n                        updates.\n  --complete COMPLETE   Compatibility alias: append the provided item to\n                        Completed.\n  --current CURRENT     Set the new Current item\n  --promote-next        Promote the first Next item into Current.\n  --next NEXT           Replace Next list; repeat for multiple items.\n  --append-completed APPEND_COMPLETED\n                        Append an item to Completed; repeat for multiple\n                        items.\n  --append-evidence APPEND_EVIDENCE\n                        Append an item to Evidence; repeat for multiple items.\n  --set-blocker SET_BLOCKER\n                        Replace Blockers with the provided item(s).\n  --clear-blockers      Clear Blockers.\n\n__OPENCLAW_ACTIVE_TASK_SHOW__\n{\