{"type":"message","id":"727c3ead","parentId":"57dcbcb1","timestamp":"2026-03-28T12:17:03.098Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Exploring audio extraction options**\n\nI’m considering if moviepy or imageio-ffmpeg can extract audio after I pip install them. I could install imageio-ffmpeg and openai-whisper, potentially using them together for extraction. The whisper library insists on ffmpeg commands, but imageio-ffmpeg can provide the binary path. I might set the IMAGEIO_FFMPEG_EXE environment variable for WAV extraction. For song lyrics in Chinese, I wonder if generic ASR will work well, but if the song has clear vocals, it might be fine. I’ll also check my pip packages for whisper.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_075abb85efaf918e0169c7c6b4efbc819aaee3cf94726d2f81\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpx8a-LQ4wnQ7d0G9K8AdThXHI78ghBH1aAHBSdorSGDN0fcLtJO3P9hyFy66F7wBSBTKowvARMWDPNBl96_vvxao99wWWnJW3VrhVdGgIAZ6msNgBK02d17zqAu7YnjxGcwf16Yr247M_w4mdLeVXmn01T7eiTjn1HmdnvEXev1q5oI1zmGTYXRO9h6j1GOLeXrj5tM16Ac40jnSENugU4--rEg6EH6emaB87ZWNj3ooFXCR2SIJ4S9UPRrLGCl50QDzYf5vI6Vh-LoHnyzSWqup9O7sOEKHeutlsDPrDS1DIQho3KN8m2GbL_N_R0VBoo_cZ9mWvW3hTojuEBlvzmsuaPin_dR0D0o2Vt8mzlcZmHqlbffaz06r7lZhy5hYbdVu7xdDapK06yH3zNPzpWrPZBT1LikYVkW7Ha0D5Ea7fgDbj4J31-HpcihhkFjSJYCnHf2RiF4oazquoRaXQpzf7BcREPTv8vk48ziXZ0txdsNTRao70gr3KJTSxA30MyFqvJmYC-gq0rn1vKCMqNyaelJOHFy3kjdkSPwKeoNdo2tXdk7_Au-y9YfMJXAmJs74MJ85hTH9fiZZETZ57gb4jbUSFShU9986qCeQUzxIThOvjxF-mkCwhVsLWfPgLLfeJHE-ixr04WJyeLhgP64N6fxhzpkt5CG90UrpvfPXA-fHWyKwHQS2peRnGdy5icyzqBak6L_uM7oHC0v4VGkxrCax_-bTHVmDSgF5hVxBEk3tNp4OHe2mMRxcwedhmEsJTTbAus3p2U0yl41u4Oj_qA4CvZyPleT3Eks46vpy3qyXz_UwykzsNUGhVtYLn4hRqHUUQM2rffIcJwFOUwia-Qu8t93VDhUg6f6A9jRHO3lRCA41PwnJylj3NJWFp-0PCCB6Vp5d6Dp5Y3yX4xeANSKd_oi35DiIny9QRqnXo1DzRCQJnOU-XWAjItDyIqJTqBF7rLyI429BJU_2vTKdiWor7yLzstenFFlQB0nShn4jscCPLOr0EvMI7wodPq0ttePHX8NHmqWkivMGPgEttYTYZXt67AQsvjB61PKzwWAHyk5IL0hSrVxkoIL9j0r5q8CFQvkH7Sd2tbhZKX_vUFjMGrlosbD-