xt\":\"**Exploring audio extraction options**\\n\\nI’m considering if moviepy or imageio-ffmpeg can extract audio after I pip install them. I could install imageio-ffmpeg and openai-whisper, potentially using them together for extraction. The whisper library insists on ffmpeg commands, but imageio-ffmpeg can provide the binary path. I might set the IMAGEIO_FFMPEG_EXE environment variable for WAV extraction. For song lyrics in Chinese, I wonder if generic ASR will work well, but if the song has clear vocals, it might be fine. I’ll also check my pip packages for whisper.\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_DCPlnSJQiYoYGHwe9ux3ycA0|fc_075abb85efaf918e0169c7c6be6d00819ab1dad1c5fcac0be1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nimport pkgutil\nmods=['torch','whisper','openai','transformers','faster_whisper','mlx_whisper','ffmpeg','imageio_ffmpeg','moviepy','pydub','librosa','soundfile']\nfor m in mods:\n    print(m, bool(pkgutil.find_loader(m)))\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":40,"yieldMs":4000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 - <<'PY'\\nimport pkgutil\\nmods=['torch','whisper','openai','transformers','faster_whisper','mlx_whisper','ffmpeg','imageio_ffmpeg','moviepy','pydub','librosa','soundfile']\\nfor m in mods:\\n    print(m, bool(pkgutil.find_loader(m)))\\nPY\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\",\"timeout\":40,\"yieldMs\":4000}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":443,"output":490,"cacheRead":82688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83621,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774700209948,"responseId":"resp_075abb85efaf918e0169c7c6b3e6bc819aa2dca91349bcd105"}}
