{"type":"message","id":"1c22d3aa","parentId":"181fc5ea","timestamp":"2026-03-28T12:22:22.039Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_IKLP5k6xhTz7CPEUoA9aeNgE|fc_075abb85efaf918e0169c7c7f89364819aa8cc25b3a1b43e51","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## frame_000_0s.jpg\n腾讯视频\n\n## frame_001_10s.jpg\n謄讯视频\n\n## frame_002_20s.jpg\n腾讯祕\n\n## frame_003_30s.jpg\n腾讯视频\n晋得道之人\n\n## frame_004_40s.jpg\n腾讯视频\n吉得道这人\n孟成之宏\n紫薇花开满城芬芳\n\n## frame_005_50s.jpg\n謄讯视频\n用智慧放\n\n## frame_006_60s.jpg\n腔批血（春凤\n\n## frame_007_70s.jpg\n腔热血\n春风暖\n\n## frame_008_80s.jpg\n腾讯视频\n面向世界 育栋梁\n\n## frame_009_90s.jpg\n(no text)\n\n## frame_010_100s.jpg\n我们的追\n\n## frame_011_110s.jpg\n腾讯视频\n让梦想追随阳光\n\n## frame_012_120s.jpg\n眷讯视频\n坐求真心堡\n\n## frame_013_130s.jpg\n而向未来。。去运粒\n\n## frame_014_140s.jpg\n腾讯视频\n崇礼友善心灵 美\n\n## frame_015_150s.jpg\n去远航\n\n## frame_016_160s.jpg\n蹈\n汙讯砂频\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774700542029}}
{"type":"message","id":"869e3590","parentId":"1c22d3aa","timestamp":"2026-03-28T12:22:45.906Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Improving OCR for subtitles**\n\nI’m working on improving the OCR process, focusing on subtitles. Cropping the bottom center where the subtitles are seems like a good idea, and I think capturing frames every one to two seconds instead of every ten could help. Using Vision to target the subtitle region might be the key. I’ll update the steps to extract frames every two seconds, and I’ll also consider cropping the lower 40%. Let’s see how the subtitles change over time!\n\n**Planning Swift Direct OCR**\n\nI need to write a Swift script for direct OCR from video. This aims to simplify the process and make it more efficient. By focusing on extracting text directly from video frames, I can streamline the workflow. I'm considering utilizing AVAssetImageGenerator for frame extraction and Vision for OCR processing. This way, I can capture subtitles or text more accurately. Let's dive into coding this and see how effective it is!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_075abb85efaf918e0169c7c802abac819abe9e842b946ee11e\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpx8gK8psF7bcAdbZq0OfDHqzDaT0OcIjao99Ofu5YyCTgTRZWv23Ya5qQERKyyajStBgoXLn7-FmzGs5pmtKAAXip297SCfMubZke9ksRAJqeN8sWuwRkn-EpzDER9yk9MtuuG02JaZYqOaXu0Qt5v-s4SAEFQ6tuNflmXWk5KzRAKItLVYfA0MZ8VmOtYB2hoYJAXUGjAm-4n1tM2LKdgyG0T0Xt2FcYIwWlyZ3hEiASzquhTPRlfEO50f3FjMEBA_r6zvfLwhQM4RD0TpEpo4KncCyotAvgX8id1zqO-Ko1siDkN3C0VcABPizNNspJ-wj5GYcDB1mCEqMasl1CWIDre54mpG6tSAjLYHPdaTHXwFxYHUGshj0hkzwPFiQg_HYCHzpECrgxIn9niH0SNPqdx8qJE4tEKmHAF2dGzehZ2r50EodMxlush9JhHwzLf46tIjHjrWTKGCVlb6Ex7v1A6FngbdgJiPDxxDkuru4VLmCfdC_m49Fo2LC6rx-yHxwPAZErzd1Aoa-Svq1UIcdxdABrIgspgn1yB6B4T_KqnqENoWkOKvtdbKOqVNhPygUOyXWUsrdW4OuR1f6Dr7GXmxwKGDFg9Q7FEJI6MzNGRZgdrO5aPliFTlyJMEJxmqKpVneVqBLoixKA_GFaY8HUOyBO1Q88EKOwZK-L8wmJCF2xIV8f4e7LYlRsiTRpjI5Dl_Sip1orF0TSlW9tGPn_nPYp40p7TC0-D79y5fszzWXQi