{"type":"message","id":"491f576d","parentId":"f6493956","timestamp":"2026-03-28T12:23:14.795Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Revising cropping strategy**\n\nI’m realizing the crop only captures the watermark at the bottom and perhaps subtitles elsewhere. I think I should position the lyrics to the center or top of the frame. Using OCR on the full frame every 2 seconds could capture more information, but I also might consider cropping the center bottom to exclude the watermark. It seems like I need to detect where text lines are appearing using previous OCR data to filter out unwanted strings. Let’s try capturing every 2 seconds.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_075abb85efaf918e0169c7c823beec819a83ed3622a851b61a\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpx8gpnKKbr2ZWE5ZphfhdNYpCnSODMfMkoyJHZbh7ERqUnXuW-u5Qx2CjfRkSyNmsB6NbnblXAo413WbEHpeCdencULaVuKYp-Tq1ltYsYVPG0gABDOv0g2_TnNxbHCMCSNnZPD9X3RO5vLMYuZlWzte49LaVLvETPawufcDID7obP-bOVxO6Ab6nRoCysBE3RQlmmtmK9D3GpZzsHnLptZbcm_S5Zf48QazR1xTVReC7miX5P-XymNKrMHFAXIdO6jPIyINiF0VN9Qfry5JZYuzdvcMKRl8OTflKRxqmIvfzWaJ_8Qt1b52jGeRppCZjLZ7gntOauD-kNp3B2xXZoZUuxD4T-8TMiC0shReN9ATh-GcxuROSu_19QDFXW3ooftKS2hU_aI0_VvlCAA4A898IysOlNg8Yqh_xr4GFQW1lddOP100F3GrOqMTSIXE93Dcs21gin7986j9pcUuIks799GQ4ei_PPHh_FFUpuldoHHGXv_qQDMZBJc16tnFncOsnBJj8BTFKaT19LAJe1XnNxdFxw4Avl9M5vJT1l5NItCfTwwDzc0ddDqFDKcte--nBQHmS1RWzyhLveMhWWy2AL5Y4PN2alV0QmAqHrOGiNJrMxy-8AE9EAceRrligKID3j1_nHBx365ze6kXqoIri9inEevbpcwEtGW5Jb-P3aQM_mUb1ipT79fODztEt6n28Y9tjNqtvFOD4WK8TEeypQ6DJijGvuc2vWrymuP38RI56zkGkyJiuvmwz2UgNWUPIe2bIIUQfHbvNedgA0sv7qqPtP0LgzCtL30q5skqYc4RLrmhFjItdFrl30GOIuxY9MTQZr5tQ9xbMND6t8hPXliPdtC593yoPSqprrfm6aBrtVHWllXNxmC5TWfagHW_a8DYnrUPzw-SUKOnyUJ0N1EM1Zn0jgpc4ZYnAyV6xrc9Spx6zAb-uYR6lVqS1q5JmSGDWZlxYARTmqm1d6d69MCG_JY1OYcL8MZFDC7jOUVxCNCg4_vRda0AgizHB-LwveHoKSU_-PmsYTtiCmDqIrCYvmX3HRKPY-d2f1wpoxzLbC-YNFxBa6ErWVFkSC_x_6o8ARxSE47sYmd-15uvW3L7FUeD72gp7vpo8p-4kMPSWO_v-HVGbqJLCnI4pYOmu6QApjCfvSjjji9yDciiF