irect mapping for session routes, and it might need a manual unbind. Since I’m replying from the same main session, the route likely hasn’t switched. I’ll need to check documentation for channel or session bindings, as they might explain persistent bindings. I wonder if existing direct messages persist due to the active session, meaning changes might only apply to new sessions. It's necessary to clarify how messages continue to route to the main session.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Fixing session routing**\\n\\nThe user hasn't sent a message after the configuration change, except for a quick \\\"好\\\" and this one, so it seems the routing hasn’t switched. I need to dig in and figure out how to fix it. There might be a durable channel or session binding store involved, so I could check the documentation for openclaw agents bindings. I’ll look for commands like `openclaw agents bindings --help` and see if there's a need to unbind the existing session route for this direct message conversation.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"我发现一个关键点：配置虽然已经改成 `xiaoguanjia`，但这条飞书 DM 现在**还在旧的 `agent:main:feishu:direct:...` 会话里**。我继续查这个“残留会话绑定”怎么切掉。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_075abb85efaf918e0169c7d9d4527c819a9576f0d114c5b84b\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_btIvYPGw4lq74Mo8caF41P1J|fc_075abb85efaf918e0169c7d9d8e62c819a8b17953a9899a192","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -RIn \"configured bindings\\|refresh bindings per message\\|existing session\\|direct session\\|agent:main:feishu:direct\\|session binding\\|bound session\" ~/.local/share/fnm/node-versions/v22.22.0/installation/lib/node_modules/openclaw/CHANGELOG.md ~/.local/share/fnm/node-versions/v22.22.0/installation/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist docs 2>/dev/null | head -n 160","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":60,"yieldMs":5000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"grep -RIn \\\"configured bindings\\\\|refresh bindings per message\\\\|existing session\\\\|direct session\\\\|agent:main:feishu:direct\\\\|session binding\\\\|bound session\\\" ~/.local/share/fnm/node-versions/v22.22.0/installation/lib/node_modules/openclaw/CHANGELOG.md ~/.local/share/fnm/node-versions/v22.22.0/installation/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist docs 2>/dev/null | head -n 160\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\",\"timeout\":60,\"yieldMs\":5000}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_QgoYwZqRJ0jNVkEZ1IdCXtHZ|fc_075abb85efaf918e0169c7d9d8e640819a9fb2115f2afea780","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw agents bindings --help","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":40,"yieldMs":3000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"openclaw agents bindings --help\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\",\"timeout\":40,\"yieldMs\":3000}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_YeGGCnwBP3bilMphyopPWP9g|fc_075abb85efaf918e0169c7d9d8e908819a9201205203e2576c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw help | sed -n '1,220p'","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":40,"yieldMs":3000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"openclaw help | sed -n '1,220p'\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\",\"timeout\":40,\"yieldMs\":3000}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1922,"output":973,"cacheRead":69888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72783,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774705092412,"responseId":"resp_075abb85efaf918e0169c7d9c62ef0819a8662f5a577e1f8d7"}}
